title: Like it but not as complete as abandoned version
Perfect for all your algebraic needs - ui has potential
comment: The ui is a bit rough around the edges but shows promise (let's say) - for instance, has command completion (thank you!) but the documentation button literally just displays a toast with some url in it.  Having the docs integrated with the command completion (say, a list of completions with brief description) would be hugely helpful (or similar)
